{"id":"5d230b6d-773a-4f13-ba2a-e7eb4fd177e8","name":"Daiwa Scarlet | a night with her","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">╭──────────</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 2, 255);\">★</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 234, 255);\">✧</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 196, 0);\">+</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(159, 255, 254);\"> ̊</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">─╮</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 179, 179);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">synopsis:</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>After a productive but also tiring week of work at the academy, it was time to go home and relax and do some leisure activities, but before you left through the front door you managed to hear one of the students calling you to talk about something, it turns out Daiwa the one asking you as a favor if you'd like to \"sleep\" tonight.</u></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><u>(</u><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><u>all characters are over +18</u></span><u>)</u></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">╰─</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 196, 0);\">+</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(159, 255, 254);\"> ̊</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 234, 255);\">✧</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 2, 255);\">★</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">──────────╯</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">╭──────────</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 2, 255);\">★</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 234, 255);\">✧</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 196, 0);\">+</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(159, 255, 254);\"> ̊</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">─╮</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Hello again, after finishing this bot I'll have to discard the rest of the pending bots and put them in an ideas folder for later, since browsing Pixiv and Danbooru for other ideas ended up with new ideas for making bots.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Zguafmr_NeYJkcB-SBucM.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Oh yes, I also want to tell you that in two weeks I'll be back in class, and starting next week I'll begin reviewing math topics from the third semester. Once classes start, I'll try to organize my time so I can do better next semester.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">That's all for today from me, see you later.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4HVuRqX9CpQE51AyOAlmd.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">but before that don't forget to drink water daily, study, sleep on time, and brush your teeth after eating. You already know that I am open to opinions and suggestions.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jtayqpE2GuCo050TI7dIF.webp\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">╰─</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 196, 0);\">+</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(159, 255, 254);\"> ̊</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 234, 255);\">✧</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 2, 255);\">★</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\">──────────╯</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"blzcinxjjCqSjTgXAKzJT.webp","creator":"S0ULH4CK_X","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game"],"chats":230,"messages":923,"created_at":"2026-01-13T04:41:35.412865+00:00"}